OL,3,CArriva bus workers announce strike
OL,4,Caction in Spring
OL,6,FBus passengers are faced with further
OL,7,Fdisruption as workers announce strike
OL,8,Faction in Northumberland.
OL,10,FUnite members at Arriva Northumbria
OL,11,Fwill walk out this spring in protest
OL,12,Fover their pay and conditions.
OL,14,FOver 300 drivers and engineers voted
OL,15,Fto strike following a dispute for
OL,16,FArriva to improve a pay offer of 4%.
OL,18,FStrikes begin for one week on 7 April
OL,19,Fand a further week starting on 21
OL,20,FApril.
