OL,3,CArriva bus workers announce strike
OL,4,Caction in Spring
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "Arriva is behaving appallingly
OL,8,Fgiven it made millions off the backs
OL,9,Fof our members and is about to be sold
OL,10,Foff to a Miami-based private equity
OL,11,Ffirm. This employer doesn't care about
OL,12,Fits workforce and its overseas owners
OL,13,Fdon't care about the communities in
OL,14,Fthe North East.
OL,16,F"Without our members there is no bus
OL,17,Fcompany and their pay and conditions
OL,18,Fmust reflect the hard work they put in
OL,19,Fday in and day out."
