OL,3,CArriva bus workers announce strike
OL,4,Caction in Spring
OL,6,FArriva is currently owned by German
OL,7,Ftransport giant Deutsche Bahn (DB) and
OL,8,Fmade profits of #2.4 million in 2022.
OL,10,FIt is due to be sold imminently to an
OL,11,Finvestment firm called I Squared
OL,12,FCapital.
OL,14,FUnite said workers are continuing to
OL,15,Fstruggle with a cost-of-living crisis
OL,16,Fwith inflation remaining high.
